A '''diplomatic barge''' was a ship used to transport [[Diplomat/Legends|diplomats]]. Examples include the [[J-type diplomatic barge/Legends|J-type diplomatic barge]] used by [[Padmé Amidala/Legends|Padmé Amidala]] and the [[Consular-class light cruiser/Legends|''Consular''-class cruiser]] used by the [[Galactic Republic/Legends|Republic]] to transport Jedi and other ambassadors on various diplomatic missions.

